Description: Test cases for BaseGeometry class

# Test Case 1: Valid input
Test Case:
my_int = 12
width = 89
Expected Output: No exceptions should be raised

# Test Case 2: Non-integer input
Test Case:
name = John
Expected Output: [TypeError] name must be an integer

# Test Case 3: Zero value input
Test Case:
age = 0
Expected Output: [ValueError] age must be greater than 0

# Test Case 4: Negative value input
Test Case:
distance = -4
Expected Output: [ValueError] distance must be greater than 0

